{"title":"山乡夜晚","authors":["冯恩昌"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":8,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山乡夜晚（外二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冯恩昌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月光洒满庭院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香雾萦绕屋檐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电视机瓜棚底下播放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醒着农家甜蜜的夜晚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抱孙子的婆婆看得出神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纳鞋底的媳妇忘抽花线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小姑打毛衣停住银针，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉嘴衔的烟袋断了青烟……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萤火虫提灯笼穿门扇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把欢乐的情景窥探。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躲在叶缝偷望的星星醉了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溜下来，化作人们的喜泪几串！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"球场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皎洁的月亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火红的太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轮换跳荡在打谷场园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——小山村的球场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旋转姑娘彩色的衣衫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇曳小伙晒黑的脊梁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是一张日夜转动的唱片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春夏秋冬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都向八方播送农家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的欢畅！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你象一位挺秀气的少女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淡绿色纱巾把发丝笼罩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几束红艳的山花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插在储满春光的鬓角。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本来是土生土长的农家女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今也爱美了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美得人们倾心地爱恋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引来唱歌的溪水缠绕。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}